
# Prerequisite
- node.js (http://nodejs.org/)

# How to try this on WebSocket supported browser
node websocket-server-node.js/server.js
open iostat-client.html in Websocke supported browser (eg: Chrome)

# How to try this on NON WebSocket supported browser
node websocket-server-node.js/server.js

open http://localhost:10080/iostat-client.html in any browser


# Watch acitivity_monitor in action
http://screenr.com/A1U_

